commit.message:
impunit.adb: Add entries for missing units

2007-12-06  Robert Dewar  <dewar@adacore.com>

	* impunit.adb: Add entries for missing units

	* Makefile.rtl: Add new run-time units.

	* Make-lang.in:  Update dependencies.

From-SVN: r130877
